OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny mist and low cloud soon
OL,6,Fburning off to leave a dry and sunny
OL,7,Fday. Warm across Stirlingshire and the
OL,8,FTrossachs but cooler along eastern
OL,9,Fcoastal districts.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry with
OL,12,Fsome late sunshine. Then the rest of
OL,13,Fthe night will be dry although some
OL,14,Fmisty low cloud possible in the east.
OL,15,FCold.
OL,16,
OL,17,CThursday:FDry and mostly sunny
OL,18,Falthough some patchy low cloud may
OL,19,Flinger along the coast. Warm across
OL,20,Fthe west but cooler in the east with
OL,21,Fan onshore breeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
